      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, with the double-VANOS system recently serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional tactile feedback and traction. The chassis remains composed with reinforced rear subframe mounting points, addressing a common structural fatigue area. Suspension geometry is true, and the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering offers the precision expected of an M-division product. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are top-tier, making this an ideal candidate for the enthusiast who prioritizes performance and engineering integrity.",
